Diagnosis
. 
–
Face fulvous with a pair of small irregularly oval black spots; scutum dark red-brown without distinct dark patterns, postpronotal lobes yellow except posterodorsal corners fuscous, notopleura yellow, mesopleural stripe narrow equal in width to notopleuron dorsally, lateral and medial postsutural vittae absent, a narrow yellow triangle running along anterior margin of mesonotal suture with base on notopleuron; setae: 
